node.text:
The beauty of @nature via @im_yash_m. 😮 Looking how the water rise up, the winds must have been so strong and powerful at this moment. 💦

Kalu Waterfall is the highest and largest waterfall in Malshej Ghat Region, a popular destination for adventure travelers. You'll feel as if you’re watching an outdoor adventure movie! Outstanding landscapes and the pristine sound of @nature. 

Have you ever seen this @nature phenomenon on a waterfall before? 🤯

📽 @im_yash_m #nature
📍Naneghat, India
🎶 Two Feet - Quick Musical Doodles

View at Paragliding World Cup 2021 with @marcellauchoa 🪂 The Paragliding World Cup is a cross country flying competition for paraglider pilots, organized by the Paragliding World Cup Association, based in Marlens, France. Each year, the Paragliding World Cup Tour visits 5-6 different locations worldwide.

Is paragliding a sport you ever thought of trying? 🙌🏼

📽 @marcellauchoa #nature
📍 Kopaonik, Serbia

node.text:
Marine Iguanas are the only marine lizard species in the world found just in the Galápagos Islands. They can dive as deep as 30 meters (98ft) and hold their breath for 30-40 mins. 🦖

What would your reaction be if you come face to face with this guy whilst diving? 😅 

📽 @kenzokiren #nature
📍Galapagos islands, Ecuador
🎶 Petit Biscuit - Jungle

node.text:
Would you try this? 😳💦 Devil’s Pool is a natural pool of water that’s situated atop of Victoria Falls, renown for being among the largest waterfalls in the world. Right on the edge of this massive waterfall, a calm pool of water forms.

After thousands of years of erosion, many rock pools have formed near the great Victoria Falls – and one of them… right on the very edge!

Would you dare to swim here? 💦

📽 @abenafrica #nature
📍Victoria Falls, Zimbabwe
🎶 Ikson - Apart

node.text:
Traditional Turkish coffee! Have you ever tried it? ☕️ Traditionally, a cup of Turkish coffee is brewed using a pan filled with sand, heated over an open flame. The sand-filled pan allows for total control over the heat. Cups left on the surface stay warm and the heat used for brewing can be adjusted by the depth of the coffee in the sand.

Turkish coffee is very finely ground coffee brewed by boiling. Any coffee bean may be used; arabica varieties are considered best, but robusta or a blend is also used. The coffee grounds are left in the coffee when served.

📽 @glamdapper #nature
📍Cappadocia, Turkey
🎶 STAY - The Kid LAROI & Justin Bieber
